\nw[Louis]Who is your friend? There are so many trees, I
can't tell. Are they nearby?

\nw[???]The person who went with Lumis to Rimuru. It's
quite far, isn't it? Several hundred meters ahead?

\nw[Louis]Huh? Is that Fross? I heard this place was sealed
off, why are you here?

\nw[???]Well? But I'm with various people, and didn't I
get permission?
\nw[Louis]Hmmm, well, whatever. By the way, is Fee okay?

\nw[???]We should probably resupply soon, just in case.
Let's fill up before the sweep operation begins.
\nw[Louis]Okay, got it. Well then, I'll rest around here.

It looks like a corpse. It hasn't been that long
since it was defeated.
